OL,3,CFather begged to save Sara Sharif but
OL,4,Cwas told 'leave it, she's dead'
OL,6,FUrfan Sharif, 42, is on trial at the
OL,7,FOld Bailey, ITV News Reporter Ellie
OL,8,FPitt has the latest from outside court
OL,10,FSara Sharif's father tried to save his
OL,11,Fdaughter and begged for an ambulance,
OL,12,Fonly to be told "Leave it, she's
OL,13,Fdead", jurors have heard.
OL,15,FTaxi driver Urfan Sharif, 42, is on
OL,16,Ftrial at the Old Bailey accused of
OL,17,Fmurdering the 10-year-old, along with
OL,18,Fher stepmother, Beinash Batool, 30,
OL,19,Fand uncle, Faisal Malik, 29.
