OL,3,CFather begged to save Sara Sharif but
OL,4,Cwas told 'leave it, she's dead'
OL,6,FSara was found dead in bed at her home
OL,7,Fin Woking, Surrey, on August 10 2023
OL,8,Fafter Sharif called police from
OL,9,FPakistan to say he had beaten her "too
OL,10,Fmuch".
OL,12,FJurors have heard she suffered dozens
OL,13,Fof injuries, including burns and human
OL,14,Fbite marks, in what the prosecution
OL,15,Falleges was a campaign of abuse.
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, Sharif denied physically
OL,18,Fabusing and killing Sara as he began
OL,19,Fto give evidence in his defence.
