OL,3,CFather begged to save Sara Sharif but
OL,4,Cwas told 'leave it, she's dead'
OL,6,FHis barrister, Naeem Mian KC, asked:
OL,7,F"Are you responsible for the death of
OL,8,FSara Sharif?"
OL,10,FThe defendant replied: "No."
OL,12,FSharif also denied that he bit, burned
OL,13,For beat up his daughter.
OL,15,FJurors heard that Sharif initially
OL,16,Fdecided to take the blame for Sara's
OL,17,Fdeath and go to Pakistan after Batool
OL,18,Fclaimed that someone else had injured
OL,19,Fher who is not on trial.
