OL,6,FMr Mian suggested that Sharif had
OL,7,Fwrongly been cast as the "villain of
OL,8,Fthe piece" because he only disciplined
OL,9,Fher with a "slap".
OL,11,FSharif had been working when Sara
OL,12,Fcollapsed at home last August 8 and
OL,13,FBatool told him to "come home", the
OL,14,Fcourt heard.
OL,16,FMr Mian told jurors: "He came home and
OL,17,Ffound her upstairs, with Beinash
OL,18,FBatool, limp. He will tell you that he
OL,19,Fasked 'What the hell has happened?',
OL,20,Fas any one of your number would.
